## About the Project
This is a telegram bot, which can search vacancies on remotive website. It uses AI to search the vacancies, and can parse your profile(if your profile is filled in AI can do more accuracy search). 
## Techology
- Python-telegram-bot
- Alembic
- Pydantic
- SQLAlchemy(with Postgres)
- Docker & docker compose
- Pytest
## Run
1. Get telegram token from @BotFather and AI token from https://console.groq.com 
2. ```shell
    docker compose up -d --build  
   ```